<bibRefCitation author="Perkins, Thomas H." journalOrPublisher="Proceedings of the Biological Society of Washington" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1080 - 1172" title="Syllidae, principally from Florida, with descriptions of a new genus and twenty-one new species" volume="93" year="1981">Perkins (1981)</bibRefCitation>
